name: Uranium Atomic Metaball vert_Violet
description: v4w.enko - "Uranium Atomic Metaball vert_Violet" is a metaball structure generated from the uranium atomic model concept with metaball algorithm. There are 92 protons and 92 electrons in the atomic structure. The model represents the only one snapshot from the one moment of time when atoms have spontaneous holded in fixed position. Possible to scale, rotate, zoom. Augmented reality mode is included with Hicetnunc
